RT @Today is Fentanyl Prevention and Awareness Day.

As too many families know, it's past time we curb the flow of deadly fentanyl into our country.

@SenatorTimScott’s FEND Off Fentanyl Act uses economic sanctions to target the fentanyl supply chain and protect our communities. https://t.co/MIYzf3co4L

